songs.title: Shoot Shoot
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Shoot, shoot
Shoot, shoot
Shoot, shoot

[Verse 1]
Shoot that AK like that K9
'Cause homie not playin' nothin'
Chopper so cute
Look like little puppy in my lap
Smile poking out, man
Don't make the puppy talk
Walk a whole clip and
Leave you on the puppy walk
Oochie oochie walla, bitches
Shouts out to my Prada bitches
Really got the strap on 'em
Looking like I'm walking bitches
Miss me with that lead shit
Hope my dogs don't come in
And they always down to fight
'cause they love Makonnen

[Chorus]
Pull up (Shoot, shoot)
Hop out (Shoot, shoot)
Let a whole clip go (Shoot, shoot)
Pull up (Shoot, shoot)
Hop out (Shoot, shoot)
Let a whole clip go (Let a whole clip go)
Yeah, pull up (Shoot, shoot)
Hop out (Shoot, shoot)
Let a whole clip go (Shoot, shoot)
Pull up (Shoot, shoot)
Hop out (Shoot, shoot)
Let a whole clip go (Let it go, let it go)

[Verse 2]
I just met a model girl who put her life on the sill
She be out here, she be out here, she be out here getting it
Can't be a tired girl when you on hire, girl
Heart so cold but you gotta have that fire, girl
She was in Spain when somebody robbed her grandma
She was very angry, but y'all know she went H.A.M, y'all
Words on the streets was it was probably two of them
Now she got caught for buzzing Peter, Hoop, an' 'em

[Chorus]
Pull up (Shoot, shoot)
Hop out (Shoot, shoot)
Let a whole clip go (Shoot, shoot)
Pull up (Shoot, shoot)
Hop out (Shoot, shoot)
Let a whole clip go (Let a whole clip go)
Yeah, pull up (Shoot, shoot)
Hop out (Shoot, shoot)
Let a whole clip go (Shoot, shoot)
Pull up (Shoot, shoot)
Hop out (Shoot, shoot)
Let a whole clip go (Let it go, let it go)

[Bridge]
Pull up, hop out
Let it go, let it go
Pull up, hop out
Let it go, let it go

[Chorus]
Yeah, pull up (Shoot, shoot)
Hop out (Shoot, shoot)
Let a whole clip go (Shoot, shoot)

Let a whole clip go (Let a whole clip go)
Yeah, pull up (Shoot, shoot)
